<br>
The young Amazon had come to pay her respects to the great shamaness who had aided her in the claiming of her soon-to-be lands.  She stood amongst a large crowd of Amazons who, to, wanted to see Yakut.  She released her mare's reigns, and her horse knew where to go without guidance.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yakut!  Yakut!&quot; She stepped towards the woman and noticed the great change in her appearance.  Her trademark smile of cynicism fell across her lips as sarcastic thoughts filled her head.  Suddenly she raised her voice louder, &quot;Hey, Yakut!  You old crone!&quot;  Laughter played her voice when she called her aged friend. <p>Ø×××|¯A_m¯a_r¯i_c¯e_&gt;</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=amazonqueenyakut>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen Shamaness</span><br>  Posts: 310<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(4/26/03 4:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=88.topic&index=51>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/_ht_a/magickalamzn/images/yakut1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ..Amarice? o.O O.O !!!</span><hr size=1> Yakut took the seat by the fire as offered, but only moments after she sat down a familiar voice called out to her. The Queen turned her head and her green orbs fell upon Amarice. She quickly got to her feet, kissed her daughter on her forehead, and with arms open ran towards Amarice. She charged and tackled the young Amazon down to the ground. She looked down at Amarice's face with a playful smile on her face.<br>
<br>
&quot;I maybe old, but I can still run with the young of them.&quot;, she chuckled and got to her feet. The Amazon stretched out her arm and helped Amarice to her feet.<br>
<br>
&quot;How've you been, Amarice? How does Samos fair as well?&quot;, she had hoped that Amarice's lands had prospered as hers. If not, Yakut would send her best workers and herself to help out. <p>-|-Queen Yakut-|-<br>
